headline: AbbVie Partners with Chicago Cubs on "Striking Out Cancer"
summary: AbbVie (NYSE: ABBV) announced a multi-year partnership with the Chicago Cubs to support people living with cancer through a campaign called "Striking Out Cancer" which starts today when the Chicago Cubs play the Cincinnati Reds. As part of the first year of the partnership, AbbVie will make a $233 donation for every strikeout by a Chicago Cubs pitcher at home during the 2025 regular season.
